OL,4,Cactivity centre for the community
OL,6,FJennifer Bates and her mum Gill have
OL,7,Fbeen involved in Guiding since they
OL,8,Fwere girls and said the activity
OL,9,Fcentre has 'made a big difference to
OL,10,Fpeople'.
OL,12,F"We have both been to Waddow Hall and
OL,13,Fexperienced what it can give people in
OL,14,Fterms of a place of peace, a place of
OL,15,Fsanctuary, but also can challenge you
OL,16,Fin outdoor skills."
OL,18,F"We want this to be here for the
OL,19,Fcommunity for generations to come."
