OL,3,CFundraisers hope to save Waddow Hall
OL,4,Cactivity centre for the community
OL,6,F"Girlguiding trustees commissioned a
OL,7,Fproperty review, and following the
OL,8,Ffindings, trustees made the decision
OL,9,Fto sell the five activity centres to
OL,10,Fhelp financially secure the future of
OL,11,Fthe organisation."
OL,13,F"There has been historic
OL,14,Funderinvestment in the activity
OL,15,Fcentres due to financial pressures.
OL,16,FThey have been running at a loss for
OL,17,Fsome years, despite successful efforts
OL,18,Ffor years to generate more business
OL,19,Ffrom different markets.
